casebody.data:
Kathleen LANE, Plaintiff-Movant,
v.
Andrew F. LANE, Jr., Defendant-Respondent. M-436/437 September Term 2018
080720 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 11, 2019

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to file a motion for counsel fees and costs as within time (M-436) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion for counsel fees and costs (M-437) is granted in the amount of $8,466.20.
